            <div class="ld-features-grid">
                <div class="ld-feature-card"><div class="ld-feature-icon">🥁</div><h3>Live Drum Audio</h3><p>Hear every sticking pattern played back with snare, kick, hi tom, and lo tom sounds.</p></div>
                <div class="ld-feature-card"><div class="ld-feature-icon">🎼</div><h3>Music Notation</h3><p>Full drum notation rendered in real time with a live playhead indicator.</p></div>
                <div class="ld-feature-card"><div class="ld-feature-icon">🎯</div><h3>Single Measure Loop</h3><p>Click any measure to loop just that measure — perfect for isolating a tricky rhythm.</p></div>
                <div class="ld-feature-card"><div class="ld-feature-icon">⏱️</div><h3>Adjustable Tempo</h3><p>Set your BPM with a slider. The metronome click track keeps you in time at any speed.</p></div>
